---
title: Pork Sausage & Capsicum Relish Hot Dogs with Cabbage Salad & Garlic Aioli
description: There’s nothing quite like a hot dog to ring in summer. Golden pork sausages, hot from the oven, sit comfortably in toasted brioche buns with a cabbage and sweetcorn salad. A drizzle of garlic aioli and chargrilled capsicum relish ties it all together, making these hot dogs a mouth-watering fusion of tangy, savoury, and creamy goodness.
